Patricia Parris https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patricia_Parris 0 Patricia Elizabeth Parris (born October 22, 1950), also known as Pat Parris, Patty Parris, Patti Parris and Patricia E. Parris, is an American actress and voice actress who provided voice-overs for several animated television series for such studios as Hanna-Barbera, The Walt Disney Company and The Jim Henson Company. She has voice acted in television, film, radio, read-along story recordings, video games and theme park attractions.
